Package piazzapanictests.tests

Class MasterTestClass

  • java.lang.Object
    • piazzapanictests.tests.MasterTestClass
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AssemblyStationTests, ChefTests, ChopStationTests, ConstructionTest, CustomerCounterTests, CustomerTests, FoodCrateTests, HobStationTests, OvenStationTests, PathfindingTests, PowerupsTests, SaveTests, ToasterStationTests, TrashCanTests
    class MasterTestClass
extends java.lang.Object
    The master test class is used to instantiate the world, stations and chefs for testing in each of its child classes. Each child class inherits from this class in order to use its methods for testing.
    Author:
    Jack Vickers, Hubert Solecki, Azzam Amirul
